    "Moreover, incorporating SK to enhance spatial attention has improved the algorithm's performance.The adjustments, including multi-scale spatial modeling and feature weighting (fuse and scale steps), offer enhanced flexibility and selective emphasis on substantial spatial regions and channels.",
